    "is_free": false,
    "description": "在《行星毁灭》宇宙中的下一款重磅游戏，《工业毁灭》结合了备受喜爱的《毁灭》游戏的标志性实时战略与深度工厂建设，带来前所未有的多种类型的融合体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/fde66e6e473daf270cfebfbc5815f8a0.poster.avif?t=1733851725\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/fde66e6e473daf270cfebfbc5815f8a0.webm?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/fde66e6e473daf270cfebfbc5815f8a0.mp4?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>系列最新游戏</strong><br>列最新作 《行星毁灭》团队销售超过300万套，几乎十年后依然受到粉丝们的庆祝和玩乐，现在他们带着对这款流行系列的新变革回来了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/7d8717e858f60d348bc91d181a555f4d.poster.avif?t=1733851725\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/7d8717e858f60d348bc91d181a555f4d.webm?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/7d8717e858f60d348bc91d181a555f4d.mp4?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>为 RTS 战斗打造终极工厂</strong><br>成为复杂生产线的主建造者，为你的杀戮战争机器提供补给。下注泰坦级超级机器人，或全力以赴，打造终极的融合星球破坏者。创建终极杀戮小队，或加强你的炮兵，用战术核武器摧毁你的对手。选择多种多样，一切由你决定。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/a6b6143e9500bda3b4699476415dda34.poster.avif?t=1733851725\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/a6b6143e9500bda3b4699476415dda34.webm?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/a6b6143e9500bda3b4699476415dda34.mp4?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>银河单人战役</strong><br>在《工业毁灭》中，体验全新的单人故事战役！混乱军团誓要用他们的柴油燃料军队摧毁银河系，撕裂并燃烧任何胆敢反抗他们的人！<br><br>我们听到了你对《行星毁灭》的反馈！在这次完整的战役体验中，你将扮演指挥官，站起来阻止毁灭，夺取银河系，每次任务都充满激动人心的体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/8eb584ff08d3d7c1df2aa4e4e6fe5075.poster.avif?t=1733851725\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/8eb584ff08d3d7c1df2aa4e4e6fe5075.webm?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796720/extras/8eb584ff08d3d7c1df2aa4e4e6fe5075.mp4?t=1733851725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多个派系</strong><br>从两个独特的派系中选择其一进行游戏或对抗 - 混乱和机械派系。每个派系都有其独特的战斗单位、游戏风格和策略。",
